{"tid":1305402,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"2019年《施政報告》公眾諮詢開始啦！","createTime":"2019-07-11T00:21:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-13T09:00:22.000Z","uid":144018,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"4cd80756597450f56e8fd1554c692f77f58fbaf2","tid":1305402,"uid":144018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T00:21:30.000Z","msg":"特區政府今日（七月十日）就二○一九年《施政報告》展開公眾諮詢。行政長官林鄭月娥、政務司司長張建宗和財政司司長陳茂波會陸續與不同界別人士會面，聽取他們的意見。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥說：「要持續發展經濟，改善民生，需要我們一起籌謀，同心協力。我誠邀各位市民就《施政報告》發表意見，讓我們可以集思廣益，制訂切合市民需要的政策措施。我和我的團隊會<span style=\"color: red;\">虛心聆聽廣大市民的聲音</span>，並在我的第三份《施政報告》中作出回應。」<br />\n<br />\n<del>據悉，有議員問及取消強積金對沖、「明日大嶼」計畫、空置稅等爭議政策會否「暫緩」，林鄭回應指會繼續推行，但會加強公眾解說及宣傳工作</del><br />\n<br />\n連登仔有咩想同親愛既特首講呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n記得電郵去policyaddress@pico.gov.hk<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n記得我哋從未成功爭取到任何嘢，一路比人帶緊遊花園同「暫緩」咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>七大訴求　缺一不可</strong><br />\n一、徹底撤回修例<br />\n二、收回暴動定義<br />\n三、撤銷對今為所有反送中抗爭者控罪<br />\n四、徹底追究警隊濫權情況<br />\n五、以行政命令解散立法會，立即實行雙真普選<br />\n六、要求永不落實「社會信用評分系統」<br />\n七、要求移除全港「多功能智慧燈柱」<br />\n<code>八、要求永不落實「明日大嶼」計畫　（私人加既）</code>"},{"pid":"a3873b626e611fb8c9eff41306ebb89f94c44afd","tid":1305402,"uid":159417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T00:31:46.000Z","msg":"我無野講"},{"pid":"9c4d6c70c7462ceb7b2e9d8547c638723242ae9c","tid":1305402,"uid":144018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T00:33:43.000Z","msg":"今年仲有Facebook（<a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/PolicyAddress2019）同Instagram（www.instagram.com/policyaddress2019）\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FPolicyAddress2019%EF%BC%89%E5%90%8CInstagram%EF%BC%88www.instagram.com%2Fpolicyaddress2019%EF%BC%89&d=GTvhkYpGRy3WajvnblfJnYhgI2KbCNwkzH4ce58ZUDE%3D&h=5d5e3bcf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.facebook.com/PolicyAddress2019）同Instagram（www.instagram.com/policyaddress2019）</a><br />\n岩哂一班鍵盤戰士<br />\n<br />\n<del>政府消息人士說，政府現時政治能量低，要思考如何做到在不會挑起政治爭拗下，令公眾明白政府仍然是向前行，處理民生、經濟議題。消息人士舉例，預料具爭議的「明日大嶼」計劃將「路難行」，但政府仍要思考其他解決土地短缺問題的辦法，同時不挑起社會神經</del><br />\n<br />\n係時候要反Cup！"},{"pid":"be94e67985f5b753d0429321d5464b7d76a52116","tid":1305402,"uid":148987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T00:34:02.000Z","msg":"(置頂) 真普選抗爭三部曲<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1303217\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1303217</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"b1726154ad2e6e2a88d9e5000a1807c65e8cf1a5","tid":1305402,"uid":25831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T00:35:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ba8595da775294f889a10c8fce42c2d3b3ad4480","tid":1305402,"uid":197086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T00:43:23.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"7a00220702af5d5759d37554d7086c498690b248","tid":1305402,"uid":144018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T01:12:45.000Z","msg":"自Pish"},{"pid":"8652af8e731484b2ff3e4a5487cf22ca8b856cc5","tid":1305402,"uid":229369,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T01:19:46.000Z","msg":"要求林鄭月娥壽終正寢！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"112be65b56df7bc754ab628112e5dc660104f083","tid":1305402,"uid":144018,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8652af8e731484b2ff3e4a5487cf22ca8b856cc5","tid":1305402,"uid":229369,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T01:19:46.000Z","msg":"要求林鄭月娥壽終正寢！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T01:28:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />警務署搞政變"},{"pid":"8db4c7adcea5b3b8064eedf5627cc7b7dfe1b5d9","tid":1305402,"uid":159913,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T01:29:35.000Z","msg":"又係加強解說，佢老味<br />\n只會嚟得更凶狠，而家香港人千祈唔好放過佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n============================<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><br />\n【團結】無大台嘅抗爭，我哋應該無時無刻激烈咁互屌。但冷靜之後要記得我哋係同路人<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1305309\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1305309</a></span>"},{"pid":"ff90cba8ac16d917baad95e2eedebcec26211713","tid":1305402,"uid":144018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8db4c7adcea5b3b8064eedf5627cc7b7dfe1b5d9","tid":1305402,"uid":159913,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T01:29:35.000Z","msg":"又係加強解說，佢老味<br />\n只會嚟得更凶狠，而家香港人千祈唔好放過佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n============================<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><br />\n【團結】無大台嘅抗爭，我哋應該無時無刻激烈咁互屌。但冷靜之後要記得我哋係同路人<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1305309\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1305309</a></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T01:30:45.000Z","msg":"其實佢有無諗過<br />\n佢只會越講越衰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"781436fd5efbe573580dfcb5abdd4ccf2fb7bc0d","tid":1305402,"uid":123069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T09:00:22.000Z","msg":"就俾佢聽下市民的聲音 一齊寄爆佢!!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img sr